I found this when working on [DASHMACROS-16|https://studio.plugins.atlassian.com/browse/DASHMACROS-16]. If you pass a list of labels to the {{\{space\}}} macro, it does between 1-3 queries per label that you pass in. See {{SpacesListMacro#getSpacesForLabels}}

